#: lib/daily_logos_web/controllers/page_html/about.html.heex:49
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "The classical Stoics form the backbone of the collection: Marcus Aurelius, Epictetus, and Seneca account for a large share of the quotes. But the collection also reaches further, drawing on modern writers and thinkers who have engaged seriously with Stoic ideas. Ancient or contemporary, the common thread is practical wisdom that actually holds up."
msgstr ""

#: lib/daily_logos_web/controllers/page_html/support.html.heex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Daily Logos is a passion project bringing Stoic wisdom into your daily life. Your support helps keep this timeless wisdom accessible to everyone."
